high_descs: Turn around and step forward to face the side of the bed.
Pick up the closest media device on the bed.
Turn left to face the night stand beside the bed.
Place the media device in the drawer of the night stand.
Turn right to face the side of the bed.
Pick up the media device on the bed.
Turn left to face the night stand beside the bed.
Place the media device in the drawer of the night stand with the other media device.
anns.task_desc: To move two media devices to the drawer of the night stands.

high_descs: go to the bed that is behind you next to the night stand.
Pick up the cell phone on the right that's on top of the bed.
go to the night stand on your right
Place the cell phone in the front left side of the top drawer of the night stand
go to the bed that is on your right next to the night stand.
Pick up the cell phone from the top of the bed.
go to the night stand on your right
Place the cell phone in the front left side of the top drawer of the night stand next to the existing phone.
anns.task_desc: place two phone  in the front left side of the top drawer of the night stand

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk up to the bed.
Pick up the leftmost phone off of the bed.
Turn right and walk towards the door, then hang a right and take a step forward, turn right again to face the wall.
Open the upper drawer of the nightstand in front of you and put the phone inside, then close the drawer.
Walk forward, then turn right and walk up to the bed.
Pick up the phone off of the bed.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn right and walk towards the wall, turn right again to face the small wooden nightstand.
Open the upper drawer of the nightstand and put the phone inside, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put two phones in a drawer.
